          "fileType": "crew",
          "title": "CREW MANIFEST",
          "content": "01 Ethan Hale\n02 Maya Chen\n03 Grant Walker\n04 Rivera Torres\n05 Owen Park\n06 Sarah Owens",
          "caption": "Official crew manifest recovered from the station database.",
          "source": "STATION_DATABASE",
          "tags": [
            "crew",
